373
00:27:51,669 --> 00:27:53,340
<font color="yellow">Aku juga dengar...</font>

374
00:27:53,340 --> 00:27:56,209
<font color="yellow">...dia mengakui cintanya
pada teman lain hari ini.</font>

375
00:27:57,380 --> 00:27:59,880
<font color="yellow">Aku mencintaimu.
Sangat mencintaimu.</font>

376
00:28:01,150 --> 00:28:03,179
<font color="yellow">Lalu kenapa kau tinggal bersamanya?</font>

377
00:28:03,850 --> 00:28:06,489
<font color="yellow">Itu karena aku ibu Yool.</font>

378
00:28:08,719 --> 00:28:09,759
<font color="yellow">Ibu Borg.</font>

379
00:28:10,189 --> 00:28:13,360
<font color="yellow">Pak Guru, aku bisa minta sesuatu?</font>

380
00:28:13,489 --> 00:28:15,030
<font color="yellow">Ya, katakan saja.</font>

381
00:28:15,030 --> 00:28:17,229
<font color="yellow">Aku akan membantumu sebisaku.</font>

382
00:28:17,229 --> 00:28:20,370
<font color="yellow">Aku menganalisis
semua wahana utama...,</font>

383
00:28:20,370 --> 00:28:22,769
<font color="yellow">...tapi aku penasaran
dengan yang belum kita lihat.</font>

384
00:28:23,370 --> 00:28:24,400
<font color="yellow">Apa?</font>

385
00:28:25,239 --> 00:28:26,409
<font color="yellow">Di mana itu?</font>

386
00:28:32,509 --> 00:28:34,780
<font color="yellow">Karena ini bukan
wahana ekstrim...</font>

387
00:28:34,780 --> 00:28:36,479
<font color="yellow">...kau bisa masuk ke dalam, bukan?</font>

388
00:28:36,679 --> 00:28:39,290
<font color="yellow">Tentu. Aku tidak apa-apa.</font>

389
00:28:39,519 --> 00:28:40,550
<font color="yellow">Ayo masuk.</font>

390
00:28:42,590 --> 00:28:43,590
<font color="yellow">Ya.</font>

391
00:28:51,199 --> 00:28:52,269
<font color="yellow">Apa ini?</font>

392
00:28:53,100 --> 00:28:54,969
<font color="yellow">Ada monster mengarah ke jam empat.</font>

393
00:28:55,699 --> 00:28:57,669
<font color="yellow">Astaga.</font>

394
00:28:57,939 --> 00:29:00,409
<font color="yellow">Nona, aku ibu Borg.</font>

395
00:29:02,939 --> 00:29:04,439
<font color="yellow">Astaga.</font>

396
00:29:04,610 --> 00:29:06,280
<font color="yellow">Ada hantu di situ!</font>

397
00:29:06,310 --> 00:29:08,479
<font color="yellow">Pak Guru, tidak apa-apa.</font>

398
00:29:08,749 --> 00:29:10,380
<font color="yellow">Ibu Borg, tunggu aku.</font>

